  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Le Terra Nova is a well placed hotel in Plagne Centre with skiing to the door and a chairlift departing from next to the hotel. Offered on a half board basis, it is a great choice for families with the children's clubs, family rooms sleeping up to four and interconnecting room, and particularly the great location on the slopes. Also keen skiers looking to discover the massive Paradiski ski area.</p>]]></listingDescription>
