  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>Fantastic location in Plagne Centre with a red and a blue piste going to the hotel and a chairlift departing right next door.</li>
<li>Our partner ski hire shop is onsite and the ski school meeting place is just 100m from the hotel.</li>
<li>There is a good selection of bars and shops close by.</li>
<li>There is also a free bus or navette service from Plagne Centre to Belle Plagne, Bellecote and Plagne 1800 every day from approx. 8.30am to 11.45pm. </li>
</ul>]]></locationDescription>
